# Custom binding
map <enter> shell
map <esc>   :unselect; clear
map r reload
map . set hidden!
map c clear
map gd bottom
map gu top

map DD delete
map PP paste
map XX cut
map CC copy
map RR rename

map mf mkfile
map md mkdir
map au unarchive
map az zip
